{"tid":1941281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湖北和武漢將解封　滯留港人稱沒「綠碼」離開有困難","createTime":"2020-03-24T10:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:37:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf86730dd1316c5eb75a82762905e90be34eb109","tid":1941281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"湖北省當局公布，武漢以外地區在明日凌晨零時起將會「解封」，解除離開湖北通道的管控措施，離開湖北的人要有湖北健康碼「綠碼」，武漢則會在4月8日「解封」。<br />\n<br />\n有身處湖北恩施的香港居民說，會嘗試找方法返回香港，但持有回鄉證的港人並無「綠碼」，離開可能有困難。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77833ab5b580f48f597cc38a6a6d810ed0a740e5","tid":1941281,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"世界欠了武漢一粒核彈！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pixfeeds.com/uploads/images/1/44/5296534-1280_936338912-nuclear-bomb-detonation.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpixfeeds.com%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F1%2F44%2F5296534-1280_936338912-nuclear-bomb-detonation.jpg&h=065d7aba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cd31e1b2d9649d5892d132fb39900cf576cf641","tid":1941281,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"解封武漢但無解封湖北 , 支那策略係逼晒啲病毒喺湖北直到感染啲人死晒為止"},{"pid":"dc936c1976582b5ddb67d85f467782158b339c2b","tid":1941281,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"正呀，二次爆發黎料"},{"pid":"08117d89ffe3d434785b2ea3b274e9f055fcd3c8","tid":1941281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc936c1976582b5ddb67d85f467782158b339c2b","tid":1941281,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"正呀，二次爆發黎料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"我已經唔識數係二次爆發定三次爆發<img src=\"